Description
-----------

This CVar highlights polygon edges.

Usage
-----

At the console type...

    r_showTris [Int]

Parameters
----------

-   [Int]
    -   0 - Disable.
    -   1 - Enable for visible surfaces.
    -   2 - Enable for front faces.
    -   3 - Enable for front and back faces.

