Notes
-----

This CVar is helpful in determining polycounts in a given scene,
investigate compilation problems and the efficiency of visportals. See
also the [r\_useScissor](R_useScissor_%28cvar%29 "R useScissor (cvar)")
and
[r\_showLightCount](R_showLightCount_%28cvar%29 "R showLightCount (cvar)")
